  "secText": [
    "  <b>Essential Question: </b>  <br />How can we describe fusion and fission?",
    "  <b>Enduring Understandings:</b>  <b>    <br />  </b>1. <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='22' data-topic='3' data-subtopic='1' data-subsection='0'>Fusion</a> is defined as when two less stable, lighter nuclei combine to form a more stable, heavier nuclei. The reaction releases energy.<br />2. <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='22' data-topic='3' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='0'>Fission</a> is defined as a heavier, less stable nuclei dividing into lighter, more stable nuclei. The reaction releases energy and neutrons.",
    "  <b>Vocabulary:</b>  <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='22' data-topic='3' data-subtopic='1' data-subsection='0'>fusion</a>, <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='22' data-topic='3' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='0'>fission</a>",
    "  <b>STEM Skills:</b>  <b>    <br />  </b>1. Review the <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='22' data-topic='0' data-subtopic='3' data-subsection='0'>nucleus</a>.<br />2. Review <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='22' data-topic='1' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='0'>unstable nuclei</a>."
